&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vendor Profile Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Complete supplier information repository&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Procurement Terms Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Payment terms and conditions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supplier Performance Tracking&lt;/strong&gt; - Quality and delivery monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vendor Categorization&lt;/strong&gt; - Classification and segmentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Integration&lt;/strong&gt; - Accounts payable and payment processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
