&lt;li&gt;Multiple contact persons per supplier&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supplier communication and interaction history&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document attachments and certifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supplier capabilities and specializations&lt;/li&gt;
